import React from 'react';
import '../style/museumlist.css'
import { Tabs } from 'antd';
const { TabPane } = Tabs;
function callback(key) {
    console.log(key);
}
export const museumlist0= 
    <Tabs defaultActiveKey="1" onChange={callback}>
        <TabPane tab="全国" key="1">
        Content of Tab Pane 1
        </TabPane>
    </Tabs>
